The paper discusses the fundamentals of Recurrent Neural Networks (RNN) and Long Short Term Memory (LSTM) networks, which are commonly used in machine learning for tasks such as natural language processing and image recognition. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). However, the paper also covers topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
